data.description: Assumable VA loan on this one. 2.25% Interest rate. Perfectly quiet Cul-de-sac home in NW Longmont. First time on the market in 53 years. Home was updated at one point and will need a roof (shingles are 3 tabs). Sellers are selling in its "AS-IS" condition. Furnace and water heater is newer.4 bed 2 bath 2 car attached. Beautiful custom wood clad windows on the main floor, Maple cabinets and a large gas stove with a gorgeous hood vent. Hard wood floors on the main that have been covered up for the last 54 yrs. Come take a look, can close quickly.
